'''提摩西·布萊克·尼爾森'''（{{lang-en|Timothy Blake Nelson}}，{{bd|1964年|5月11日}}）是一位[[美國|美國]]男演員、編劇和導演。出演過的著名作品如電影《[[霹靂高手|霹靂高手]]》（2000年）、《[[別有洞天|別有洞天]]》（2003年）、《[[諜對諜|諜對諜]]》（2005年）及《[[無敵浩克|無敵浩克]]》（2008年）。

== 早期生活 ==
尼爾森出生於[[俄克拉何馬州|俄克拉何馬州]][[塔爾薩|塔爾薩]]的一個[[猶太|猶太]]家庭<ref>{{cite web|url=http://aboutfilm.com/features/greyzone/feature.htm|title=Feature Article and Interviews - THE GREY ZONE (2001)|publisher=Aboutfilm.com|accessdate=2014-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111002033337/http://aboutfilm.com/features/greyzone/feature.htm|archive-date=2011-10-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Bloom|first=Nate|title=Jewish stars: Whales, ghosts and ‘Smash’|publisher=Cleveland Jewish News|date=2012-02-02|url=https://www.clevelandjewishnews.com/archives/jewish-stars-whales-ghosts-and-smash/article_77b968c0-4dde-11e1-a4ef-0019bb2963f4.html|accessdate=2018-04-16|archive-date=2018-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180506220459/https://www.clevelandjewishnews.com/archives/jewish-stars-whales-ghosts-and-smash/article_77b968c0-4dde-11e1-a4ef-0019bb2963f4.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。母親露絲·尼爾森（Ruth Nelson）的娘家姓為凱瑟（Kaiser）<ref name="TW060509">Michael Smith, [http://www.tulsaworld.com/spot/article.aspx?subjectid=243&articleid=20090506_282_D10_Thenew625933 "Bloomer Sooner: Tulsa native Tim Blake Nelson's roots are showing"], ''Tulsa World'', 2009-05-06.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jewishmuseum.net/other/images/muse.pdf|title=Archived copy|accessdate=2007-09-27|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111001110522/http://www.jewishmuseum.net/other/images/muse.pdf|archivedate=2011-10-01}}</ref>，是塔爾薩地方著名的社會活動家和慈善家，而父親唐·尼爾森（Don Nelson）則是名地質學家<ref>Tulsa Historical Society, [http://www.tulsahistory.org/hof/nelson.html 1999 Hall of Fame Inductee: Ruth K. Nelson] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090126213615/http://www.tulsahistory.org/hof/nelson.html|date=2009-01-26}}, tulsahistory.org; accessed June 14, 2017.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tulsaworld.com/archives/native-tulsan-featured-in-miniseries-tim-nelson-makes-leap-from/article_26a35455-cdb7-5ad9-853d-b7abf7c4a7cf.html|title=Native Tulsan Featured in Miniseries: Tim Nelson Makes Leap From Shakespeare to `Dead Man's Walk'|first=Rita|last=Sherrow|publisher=tulsaworld|access-date=2018-09-14|archive-date=2021-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210610111955/https://tulsaworld.com/archives/native-tulsan-featured-in-miniseries-tim-nelson-makes-leap-from/article_26a35455-cdb7-5ad9-853d-b7abf7c4a7cf.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的叔叔是美國著名商人{{le|喬治·凱瑟|George Kaiser}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jweekly.com/2015/08/06/celebrity-jews0807|title=Celebrity jews|author=Bloom, Nate|date=2015-08-06|publisher=jweekly.com|accessdate=2018-04-16|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927201905/https://www.jweekly.com/2015/08/06/celebrity-jews0807/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

尼爾森的祖父母來自[[德國|德國]]，在[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]前不久逃離[[納粹|納粹]]，於1938年移居[[英國|英國]]，後於1941年移民至美國<ref name=NPRgrey>{{cite web|url=https://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=1152404|title='The Grey Zone'|publisher=NPR|date=2002-10-26|accessdate=2014-07-15|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001055857/https://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=1152404|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bluntreview.com/reviews/blake.htm|title=Archived copy|accessdate=2007-09-27|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111002031656/http://www.bluntreview.com/reviews/blake.htm|archivedate=2011-10-02}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/jonathan-valania/o-brother-who-art-thou-a-_b_3001892.html|title=Jonathan Valania: O Brother Who Art Thou? A Q&A With Actor/Writer/Director Tim Blake Nelson|publisher=Huffingtonpost.com|date=2013-04-03|accessdate=2013-07-01|archive-date=2016-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530160257/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/jonathan-valania/o-brother-who-art-thou-a-_b_3001892.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他父親的家人是{{le|俄羅斯猶太人的歷史|History of the Jews in Russia|俄羅斯猶太人}}的移民<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=WT&p_theme=wt&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0F6F9FF3E0B2D6ED&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|title=People adapt to 'Grey Zone' Jewish workers in Nazi camp|work=The Washington Times|accessdate=2014-07-15|archive-date=2018-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180902151621/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=WT&p_theme=wt&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0F6F9FF3E0B2D6ED&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

他曾就讀位於俄克拉何馬州{{le|隆沃爾夫 (俄克拉何馬州)|Lone Wolf, Oklahoma|隆沃爾夫}}{{le|石英山度假村藝術和會議中心|Quartz Mountain Resort Arts and Conference Center}}的俄克拉何馬暑期藝術學院<ref>Oklahoma Arts Institute, [http://oaiquartz.com/alumni/listing.cfm Alumni Listing] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070825111930/http://www.oaiquartz.com/alumni/listing.cfm|date=2007-08-25|accessdate=2009-01-21}}</ref>。

1982年，尼爾森從畢業於塔爾薩的{{le|霍爾霍爾 (俄克拉何馬州)|Holland Hall (Tulsa, Oklahoma)|霍爾霍爾學院}}<ref name="TW060509" />。之後在[[布朗大學|布朗大學]]中作為1986年的高級演說家。他本身是{{le|優等生協會|Phi Beta Kappa}}的成員。尼爾森還憑藉著卓越的古典研究獲得了Workman/Driskoll獎<ref>Kari Molvar, [https://web.archive.org/web/20011226063441/http://brownalumnimagazine.com/storydetail.cfm?ID=61 "Q&A: Tim Blake Nelson"], ''Brown Alumni Magazine'' (March/April 2001).</ref>。19歲的他於1990年從[[茱莉亞學院|茱莉亞學院]]畢業<ref>[http://www.juilliard.edu/alumni/reflections_0603.html] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101219080312/http://www.juilliard.edu/alumni/reflections_0603.html|date=2010-12-19}}</ref>。

== 個人生活 ==
尼爾森和他的妻子麗莎·貝納維德斯（Lisa Benavides）於1994年結婚，並育有三子，他們一家住在[[紐約市|紐約市]]<ref name="TW060509" />。

